Package com.jesusnut.utils

Class ElementUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jesusnut.utils.ElementUtils
  • public final class ElementUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class having methods which can be applied on WebDriver, WebElements and Other Browser Components- e.g. Alerts, Windows etc.
    Also, manages the WebDriver Wait time.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Abhishek Bhardwaj-JesusNut
